OL,3,CDriving test backlog 'cannot get much
OL,4,Cworse'
OL,6,FLearner drivers are being forced to
OL,7,Fwait more than five months to book a
OL,8,Fslot at four out of five test centres,
OL,9,Fnew figures show.
OL,11,FSome 258 locations in Britain had the
OL,12,Fmaximum possible waiting time of 24
OL,13,Fweeks for a test as of May 5, which is
OL,14,F81% of all sites.
OL,16,FThat is up from 161 at the start of
OL,17,Fthe year.
