OL,3,CDriving test backlog 'cannot get much
OL,4,Cworse'
OL,6,FAA Driving School, which obtained the
OL,7,Ffigures from the Driver and Vehicle
OL,8,FStandards Agency (DVSA), warned the
OL,9,Fsituation "cannot get much worse".
OL,11,FThe average waiting time across all
OL,12,Ftest centres has reached 22 weeks, up
OL,13,Ffrom 14 weeks in February 2024.
OL,15,FThe DVSA attributes the backlog to an
OL,16,Fincrease in demand and some people
OL,17,Fbooking their test much earlier than
OL,18,Fbefore.
