OL,3,CDriving test backlog 'cannot get much
OL,4,Cworse'
OL,6,FOfficials hope an increase in the
OL,7,Fnumber of tests being conducted will
OL,8,Fbring waiting times down.
OL,10,FThe number of future bookings in the
OL,11,FDVSA's system was 122,000 higher in
OL,12,FJune compared with the same month last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FPublic spending watchdog the National
OL,16,FAudit Office recently announced it
OL,17,Fwill investigate the "root causes" of
OL,18,Fdelays to booking tests, and "how the
OL,19,FDVSA is responding".
