OL,3,CDriving test backlog 'cannot get much
OL,4,Cworse'
OL,6,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,7,Fsaid in April the Labour Government
OL,8,F"inherited an enormous backlog" but
OL,9,Fwas "acting fast".
OL,11,FShe told the Commons Transport Select
OL,12,FCommittee her department aimed to
OL,13,Freduce the average waiting time to
OL,14,Fseven weeks by summer 2026.
OL,16,FA Government consultation on amending
OL,17,Fthe test booking system closed last
OL,18,Fweek.
