OL,6,FThis featured a plan aimed at stopping
OL,7,Fbots mass-booking new slots so they
OL,8,Fcan be resold on the black market for
OL,9,Finflated prices.
OL,11,FThe Department for Transport also
OL,12,Finstructed the DVSA to offer
OL,13,Fadditional overtime payments to
OL,14,Fincentivise instructors to conduct
OL,15,Fmore tests.
OL,17,FStaff at the agency qualified to
OL,18,Fconduct tests are being asked to
OL,19,Fvoluntarily return to the front line,
OL,20,Fwhile the number of permanent trainers
OL,21,Ffor new examiners is being doubled.
