OL,3,CDriving test backlog 'cannot get much
OL,4,Cworse'
OL,6,FEmma Bush, managing director of AA
OL,7,FDriving School, said: "With the vast
OL,8,Fmajority of driving test centres now
OL,9,Fshowing waits at the maximum the
OL,10,Fsystem will allow, the situation
OL,11,Fcannot get much worse.
OL,13,F"New measures designed to start
OL,14,Fbringing down waiting times were
OL,15,Fimplemented at the start of April by
OL,16,Fthe DVSA.
OL,18,F"There are signs of recovery though,
OL,19,Fputting both the industry and learners
OL,20,Fon tenterhooks for more signs of
OL,21,Fimprovement in the coming months.
