OL,6,F"While we would expect these changes
OL,7,Fto take a few months to show a
OL,8,Fpositive impact, it is still
OL,9,Fdisappointing to see that learners are
OL,10,Fcontinuing to face an uphill battle
OL,11,Fwhen it comes to booking their driving
OL,12,Ftest."
OL,14,FDVSA chief executive Loveday Ryder
OL,15,Fsaid: "DVSA's goal is to make booking
OL,16,Fa driving test easier and fairer for
OL,17,Flearner drivers.
OL,19,F"We are making progress on our plans.
